private void reload(List<Set<Integer>> bucketsByLabel,List<Integer> labels,int minLabel){ if (labels.size() == 0) { return; } if (minLabel == 0) { for (int i = 0; i < bucketsByLabel.size(); i++) { bucketsByLabel.get(i).clear(); } return; } Set<Integer> bucket = bucketsByLabel.get(minLabel); if (bucket == null) { bucket = new HashSet<>(); bucketsByLabel.set(minLabel, bucket); } bucket.clear(); for (int i = 0; i < labels.size(); i++) { bucket.add(labels.get(i)); } }
